            </button>
        </h2>

        <div x-show="expanded" x-collapse>
            <div class="max-w-lg px-6 py-4 text-gray-200">
                Please contact <a href="https://mobicycle.support" class="italic text-orange-650 hover:not-italic hover:text-gray-300"> MobiCycle Support </a>.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

      <!-- QUESTION 6 -->
      <div x-data="{
        id: 6,
        get expanded() {
            return this.active === this.id
        },
        set expanded(value) {
            this.active = value ? this.id : null
        },
    }" role="region" class="rounded-lg shadow bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700">
        <h2>
            <button
                x-on:click="expanded = !expanded"
                :aria-expanded="expanded"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full px-6 py-4 text-xl font-bold rounded-t-lg shadow bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-200"
            >
                <span class="font-serif text-purple-650">How do your calculations differ from others?</span>
                <span x-show="expanded" aria-hidden="true" class="ml-4"><PlusSVG/></span>
                <span x-show="!expanded" aria-hidden="true" class="ml-4"><MinusSVG/></span>
            </button>
        </h2>

        <div x-show="expanded" x-collapse>
            <div class="max-w-full px-6 py-4 text-gray-200">
               We go beyond the Greenhouse Gas Protocol, Principal Adverse Indicators or a generic list of sustainability factors.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

      <!-- QUESTION 7 -->
      <div x-data="{
        id: 7,
        get expanded() {
            return this.active === this.id
        },
        set expanded(value) {
            this.active = value ? this.id : null
        },
    }" role="region" class="rounded-lg shadow bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-700">
        <h2>
            <button
                x-on:click="expanded = !expanded"
                :aria-expanded="expanded"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full px-6 py-4 text-xl font-bold rounded-t-lg shadow bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-200"
            >
                <span class="font-serif text-purple-650">How does your methodology differ?</span>
                <span x-show="expanded" aria-hidden="true" class="ml-4"><PlusSVG/></span>
                <span x-show="!expanded" aria-hidden="true" class="ml-4"><MinusSVG/></span>
            </button>
        </h2>

        <div x-show="expanded" x-collapse>
            <div class="max-w-full px-6 py-4 text-gray-200">
               We focus on supply chain emissions for electronics and electricals. We also account for environmental impacts due to biodiversity loss and pollution.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</section>